Entry.JapaneseText: ワン・ギンに会いにいこうヨ。 タロットを取られるワケじゃないしさ。
Entry.EnglishText: Let's go meet with Wang Gin. It doesn't mean we have to give him your cards.

Entry.JapaneseText: そうね……見せても減るもんじゃないし、 背に腹は変えられないわね。
Entry.EnglishText: You're right... Just showing them won't hurt. Besides, everything has a price.
